This paper deals with the problem of contextualizing logical statements, which is a common issue in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The specific logical system used in this paper is Description Logics, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the formalization of contextualization, which is relevant to computational linguistics (cs.CL) and cryptography (cs.CR) as well.
